<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
    />
    <meta
      http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible"
      content="IE=edge"
    />
    <meta
      name="color-scheme"
      content="light dark"
    />
    <title>Email</title>
    <link
      rel="preconnect"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"
    />
    <link
      rel="preconnect"
      href="https://fonts.gstatic.com"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #033348;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
      color: white;
    "
  >
    <div
      class="inner-div"
      style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 600px; width: 90%"
    >
      <img
        class="mitt-arv-logo"
        style="
          height: 40px;
          max-width: 136.9px;
          width: 100%;
          margin-top: 20px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        "
        src="https://mittarvtesting.blob.core.windows.net/mittarv-icons/mitt_arv_logo_horizontal.png"
        alt="Mitt Arv"
      />
      <div
        class="inner-div-bg-color"
        style="background-color: #043d55; padding: 2% 4%"
      >
        <div
          class="image-div"
          style="text-align: center"
        >
          <img
            class="alarm-ringing"
            style="
              display: inline-block;
              margin-top: 24px;
              margin-bottom: 24px;
              height: 60px;
            "
            src="https://mittarvtesting.blob.core.windows.net/mittarv-icons/alaram_ringing.png"
            alt="Alaram"
          />
        </div>
        <h2
          style="
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            color: white;
          "
        >
          Greetings
        </h2>
        <h2
          style="
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
          "
        >
          Dear {{user_name}}!
        </h2>
        <p
          style="
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: white;
          "
        >
          This is a crucial reminder about the draft you created in your
          Emotional Will platform 30 days ago. It's important to act now to
          ensure that your heartfelt messages and essential thoughts are
          preserved.
        </p>
        <div
          class="progress-bar"
          style="height: 8px; background-color: white; border-radius: 40px"
        >
          <div
            class="progress"
            style="
              height: 8px;
              width: 66%;
              background-color: #d4545c;
              border-radius: 40px;
            "
          ></div>
        </div>
        <div style="height: 5px"></div>
        <table
          style="width: 100%; border-spacing: 0; border-collapse: collapse"
        >
          <tr>
            <td
              style="
                font-size: 12px;
                font-weight: 600;
                text-align: left;
                padding: 0;
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                color: white;
              "
            >
              15 days remaining
            </td>
            <td
              style="
                font-size: 12px;
                font-weight: 600;
                text-align: right;
                padding: 0;
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                color: white;
              "
            >
              out of 45 days
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <div
          class="time-sensitive-information"
          style="margin-top: 24px"
        >
          <p style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: white;">
            Time-sensitive information:
          </p>
          <ul
            style="
              font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
              font-size: 12px;
              padding-left: 20px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: white;
            "
          >
            <li style="color: white;" >Your draft will be automatically deleted in 15 days.</li>
            <li style="color: white;" >After deletion, the content cannot be recovered.</li>
            <li style="color: white;" >This is part of our 45-day draft lifespan policy.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p style="font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; margin-block: 24px; color: white;">
          We encourage you to take action now to ensure your heartfelt messages
          and important thoughts are preserved.
        </p>
        <div
          class="time-sensitive-information"
          style="margin-top: 24px"
        >
          <p style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: white;">
            We encourage you to:
          </p>
          <ul
            style="
              font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
              font-size: 12px;
              padding-left: 20px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: white;
            "
          >
            <li style="color: white;">Log in and review your draft</li>
            <li style="color: white;">Finalize and save it if it's ready</li>
            <li style="color: white;">Continue working on it if needed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p
          style="
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 24px;
          "
        >
          Your emotional legacy is important. Don't let your thoughts and wishes
          go unrecorded.
        </p>
        <div style="height: 24px;"></div>
        <div
          class="center"
          style="
            margin: auto;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            width: 140px;
            height: 30px;
            background-color: #fd9320;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: flex;
          "
        >
          <a
            href="{{redirect_url}}"
            target="_blank"
            style="
              font-size: 12px;
              color: white;
              font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
              font-weight: 600;
              font-size: 12px;
              letter-spacing: 1.5%;
              margin: auto;
              text-decoration: none;
            "
          >
            View on Mitt Arv
          </a>
        </div>
        <p
          style="
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
          "
        >
          Warmest regards,<br />Team
          <span style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #84b5d2"
            >Mitt Arv</span
          ><br /><b>Zero - Life - Infinity</b>
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
          "
        >
          For any inquiries, kindly reach out to us
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
          "
        >
          at
          <a
            href="mailto:support@mittarv.com"
            style="color: white; text-decoration: none"
            onmouseover="this.style.color='#FD9320'"
            onmouseout="this.style.color='white'"
            >support@mittarv.com</a
          >
        </p>
        <div style="height: 32px"></div>
      </div>
      <div style="height: 56px"></div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
